{
  "stem": "25348.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She had a knack of not asking questions, not embarrassing me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But she told me she knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Remember, I confessed to her husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she said, this is between you and us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that daughter-in-law of hers got me a job at 4711.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That's the prestigious eau de cologne factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Only that during the war, they never made eau de cologne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They made-- made a kind of a soap derivative product.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I was packing what they called toothpaste substitute, [GERMAN], into boxes, which was a cushy job-- comparatively cushy job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I lived there with this lady, Frau [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Marta ?] Moebius who was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it-- the treatment-- her treatment of me was a translation of humane-- of humanness.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "She took off an old blanket from her bed to have it made into a coat for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "She took me along to her friends, as a Pole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She cared for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She cooked for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And her daughter-in-law, from the job that I was, wanted to do a favor to her dentist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And she got me into a private household.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The irony, my first impression of the household was that these people were not Nazis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I must say, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we Jews are also prejudice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always had a Polish servant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she never ate at our table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I was is a servant in that house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- she came up and she said-- she taught me how to set the table.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said what about your place?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, with Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Winkler?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Winkler, in their 25-years daughter at the one table.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "End of tape three.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
